      "text": "jeu vidéo de 2000",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikidata"
    },
    {
      "text": "NHL Blades of Steel 2000 is a set of two hockey video games published by Konami for PlayStation and Game Boy Color in 2000. A Nintendo 64 version had been planned (and was even reviewed by Game Informer while in development), but was later cancelled. NHL Blades of Steel 2000 is the third and last game in the Blades of Steel series following Blades of Steel for the NES and NHL Blades of Steel '99 for the Nintendo 64.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Blades of Steel ou NHL Blades of Steel est une série de jeux vidéo de hockey sur glace développée par Konami de 1987 à 2000.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    }
  ]
